Package: sarlacc
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2018-02-25
Title: Pipeline for Oxford Nanopore Single-Cell RNA-Seq Data Analysis
Authors@R: c(person("Florian", "Bieberich", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
        "Florian.Bieberich@cruk.cam.ac.uk"), person("Aaron", "Lun", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Florian Bieberich <Florian.Bieberich@cruk.cam.ac.uk>
Depends: R (>= 3.4), Biostrings, GenomicRanges, S4Vectors, BiocParallel
Imports: methods, utils, IRanges, XVector, muscle, BiocGenerics, 
        GenomicAlignments, igraph, Rcpp
Suggests: Rsamtools, knitr, testthat
Description: Implements a variety of low-level analyses of single-cell 
        RNA-seq data. Methods are provided for normalization of 
        cell-specific biases, assignment of cell cycle phase, and 
        detection of highly variable and significantly correlated genes.
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: yes
VignetteBuilder: knitr
